<p/>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n250/mode/1up">247</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n252/mode/1up">249</ref>.</p>
<p>ataṟkuviṉaiyuṭaimai - karumpiṟku vēli eṉpatu. viṉai īṇṭupakāram. ataṟkuṭampaṭutal - cāttaṟku makaḷuṭampaṭṭār eṉpatu. cāṉṟōr kolaikkuṭampaṭṭār eṉpatumatu. ataṟkuppaṭuporuḷāvatu potuvākiya poruḷaip pakukkuṅkāl orupaṅkiṟpaṭum poruḷ; atu cāttaṟkuk kūṟu koṟṟaṉ eṉpatu. atuvāku kiḷavi - kaṭicūttirattiṟkup poṉ eṉpatu. poṉ kaṭicūttiramāyt tiriyumākaliṉ atuvākukiḷaviyeṉṟār. kiḷavi poruḷ. ataṟkiyāppuṭaimai - kaikkiyāppuṭaiyatu kaṭakam eṉpatu. ataṟporuṭṭātal - kūḻiṟkuk kuṟṟēval ceyyum eṉpatu. naṭpu - avaṟku naṭṭāṉ; avaṟkut tamaṉ eṉpaṉa. pakai - avaṟkup pakai; avaṟku māṟṟāṉ eṉpaṉa. kātal - naṭṭārkkuk kātalaṉ; putalvaṟkaṉpuṟum eṉpaṉa.  ciṟappu - vaṭukaracarkkuc ciṟantār cōḻiyavaracar; kaṟpārkkuc ciṟantatu cevi eṉpaṉa.</p>
<p>apporuḷeṉṟatu aṉṉaporuḷai; ivvāṭaiyumannūlāṉiyaṉṟateṉṟatupōla. eṉavē, aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟavāṟām.</p>
<p>apporuṭkiḷaviyumeṉṟataṉāl, piṇikku maruntu, naṭṭārkkut tōṟkum; avaṟkut takkāḷivaḷ; uṟṟārkkuriyar poṟṟoṭimakaḷir eṉpaṉa pōlvaṉavellāṅkoḷka.	(15)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
